                            <comment id="14465229" author="shemnon" created="Mon, 25 Aug 2008 10:36:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The issue isn&apos;t the Console, the problem is that GroovyShell.evaluate(scriptText, scriptName) doesn&apos;t treat the code the same as the groovyshell run varients.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, I think the severity is overstated.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14465221" author="paulk" created="Mon, 25 Aug 2008 20:53:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I probably agree it isn&apos;t a major bug but isn&apos;t it a worthwhile enhancement request?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
